  "texts": [
    "It allows the industrial GPT bot to respond to specific queries related to the factory's state, production, and equipment.",
    "Each bot version has its front end.",
    "The offline one runs on Streamlit [52], an open-source web-based visualization tool, and the online one uses the OpenAI GPT-4 customization GPT platform as the front end.Figure 2 presents the detailed architecture of the two industrial bot versions.",
    "In the offline version, we add a Langchain agent (integrated with libraries via Python, the programming language we utilize) to decrypt the CSV file 123 Fig. 1 GPT industrial bot high-level architecture content that an LM, specialized in understanding text, does not understand and read by default.",
    "The Langchain agent acts as a bridge between the factory CSV file and the GPT-4 backend LM."
  ]
